parameters:
The game is One hour a day...!! \ For a healthy lifestyle,
it's important to maintain the right distance...! \ Oh no,
there's doodles on the sign that was written.

Don't be so noisy...!! \ We won't be bound by boring adult
rules!! \ We'll play games until we drop... Right,
everyone!? \ ...That's what it says.

......Huh, what!? You defeated it?!? How could you do such a
meaningless task for such a long time!?

\SE[102]No, when there's something like this, I can't help
but want to do my best... It's like my inner drive for
improvement ignites...

So you're the type who can defeat 'Treeguard-senpai'... no,
'The Demon of the Immortal Manor' barehanded, huh... I guess
there really are people like that... weird ones.

Just to make sure, you were probably thinking that it's not
the appropriate boss to fight... right? ...while you were
fighting, I mean...?

\SE[1]Well, it's just that... I kind of started feeling that
way halfway through...

...Well, I understand. I can't just let you work so hard for
nothing. I'll give you a small gift. You're definitely a
dedicated customer, after all...

\SE[22]Wow! There are so many things that seem quite
amazing...! \SE[5]Is it okay for me to receive something
like this? The balance and all...

You're probably going to destroy it anyway. Well then, you
might as well let me help you.
